The paper deals with facial expression recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of support vector machines for classification suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the application of facial expression recognition in cognitive science, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
